  "text": [
    "The strident high",
    "civic trumpeting",
    "of misrule. It is",
    "what we stand for.",
    "Wild insolence,",
    "aggregates without",
    "distinction. Courage",
    "of common men:",
    "spent in the ruck",
    "their remnant witness",
    "after centuries",
    "is granted them",
    "like a pardon.",
    "And other fealties",
    "other fortitudes",
    "broken as named\u2014",
    "Respublica",
    "brokenly recalled,",
    "its archaic laws",
    "and hymnody;",
    "and destroyed hope",
    "that so many times",
    "is brought with triumph",
    "back from the dead."
  ],
  "title": "Respublica",
